article.description: — Jose Placer scored 22 points as North Florida beat North Alabama 71-58 on Saturday. Jarius Hicklen added 21 points for the Ospreys.
article.headline: Placer, Hicklen carry North Florida over North Alabama 71-58
article.linkText: Placer, Hicklen carry North Florida over North Alabama 71-58
article.story: FLORENCE, Ala. -- — Jose Placer scored 22 points as North Florida beat North Alabama 71-58 on Saturday. Jarius Hicklen added 21 points for the Ospreys. Jadyn Parker had 12 points for North Florida (7-17, 3-7 Atlantic Sun Conference). Dorian James added seven rebounds. Daniel Ortiz had 14 points for the Lions (9-14, 2-8). Isaac Chatman added 13 points and 11 rebounds. Detalian Brown had 10 points. Will Soucie had a career-high 10 rebounds plus five points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
